# Buckets

| Bucket | Description |
---|:---
| ci | Local post-submit |
| global.ci | Global (based on //integration) post-submit |
| prod | Used to build prebuilts |
| toolchain.ci | Toolchain post-submit |
| tricium | Local presubmit |
| try | Local presubmit |
